(76271, 35371, 6901, 1, 'OVDS', '', '2014-05-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '1.OVDS \n宇宙般巨大的疼痛藏在心中\n此刻將自己沒收從今以後\n宇宙般巨大的疼痛\n藏在心中 躲在心中 摸不透\n此刻將自己沒收\n從今以後 哭過以後 一無所有\n宇宙般巨大的疼痛\n此刻將自己沒收\n\nTonight we set is on fire!\n\nThis one for all the fighters!\n', '', 326, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-28 15:42:36', '2015-03-12 14:07:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(76272, 35371, 6901, 2, 'Reverse The World 2014', '', '2014-05-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '2.Reverse The World 2014\nLet`s break the cycle & find a new world.\nThe faith is in your soul.\n\n不堪的新聞 充斥在你我的周圍 \n畫面總是 殘忍地荼毒著我知覺\n難道童話般幸福快樂的日子\n僅存在相片裡 像青春 一去不回\n這不是教科書 是學校沒教的書\n學不好也不能輸 我走我自己的路\n權力讓人迷失 在這利益的國度\n用手和心付出 讓這土地不再哭\n\nLet`s break the cycle & find a new world.\nThe faith is in your...\nGotta break that fucking cycle, find the new world\nLet`s break the cycle & find a new world.\nThe faith is in your...\nGot that faith into your soul and never let go\nLet`s break the cycle & find a new world.\n\n費盡力量去成全 所有的不完美\n一年年彈指歲月 習慣了妥協\n你說受比施簡單\n難道最後失去了一切 教誨才被了解\n每一天存在 這樣的社會有沒有什麼\n比自己更加珍貴還有多少時間\n要把眼光放遠 將力量凝結\n我們一起 反轉這世界\n\nLet`s do it right now!\n\nLet`s break,break the cycle.\nThe faith is in your soul.\n\nGotta break that fucking cycle, find the new world\nGot that faith into your soul and never let go,\nGotta break that fucking cycle, find the new world, yeah!\nSo let`s break the cycle.\n', '', 305, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-28 15:46:54', '2015-03-12 14:07:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(76273, 35371, 6901, 3, 'Hold Me For A Reason feat. Olivia Yan', '', '2014-05-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '3.Hold Me for a Reason feat. Olivia Yan\n在把黑暗看清以前 還輕撫你的臉 \n有潛台詞的笑容藏 一道曙光 \n被黑暗看清以前 躲在想念的背面 \n在說不出的話藏 一道淚光\n淚的光 是光 是明或昏暗 \n曾說愛 說愛 愛沒有答案 \n已不在 不再 不再有釋懷 \n還說愛 說愛 誰說愛\n\nEvery inch of your skin that I`m seek, in my memories \nBreath that you take from my space, something losing with\nSmile that you spend on these days, you deserve it \nIf this, is the way it`s got to be \nI`ll take it from here to the end of my world, we used to own it \nBut now, all the joys in between, getting blurred \nIt`s like, a cancer in my head growing slowly \nHow can a king without he`s queen \n\nHold Me for a Reason \nWe can make it a deal \nWhatever promise you made \nI have no problem to say \n\n狂戀姿態 有我的浪漫\n晝夜兩端 在你的愛旋轉\n儘管期待 是無盡的等待\n願淚中的答案 是光環\n\nHold Me for a Reason\nWe can make it a deal \n\nHold Me for a Reason\nWe’re seeking for the light\n', '', 273, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-28 15:50:17', '2015-03-12 14:07:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(76274, 35371, 6901, 4, 'Alcoholdisiac', '', '2014-05-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '4.Alcoholdiziac\nLast night, I was so drunk, can`t walk myself, then I throw up...\nand got kick out by the night club, they called me legend of the king crunk\n\nDozens of the missed call, on my phone\nWho''s that girl next to me, I don''t know\nKeep it fizzledrizzle, I''m in the zone\nThat''s how it goes, how it goes\n\nStarry night like Van Gogh, homies pop that bottle\nThe dangerous necessity of health, shit! we been on!\nGot chicks in my sight, set a box and make it right\nTonight we gon` sippin, no parental advise, Yeah~\n\nCrunked up eerrrr day, It don`t matter what It takes\nI`m just crunked up errrr-day, Alcoholdisiac I am\n\nGive me one for the sorrows, two for the ills\nThree for me to chill like I`m king of the hill (So crazy)\nTinker Bell on that, bring it on\nLine`em up, light it up let`s do this for real, yeah!\n\nWhisky, Champagne, Tequila on flame,\nOh~ We notoriously take control\n(We`re OVDS, so let''s go!)\n\nSo let`s go for blast off, we bring that hype to get soaked\nNow get loose or get lost, too fast to live don`t drink slow\nHere come`s another from that O\nIf you don`t feel like we do then you ain`t crunk for sure\nWhen we say it than we did it, got no plan b in our ROE\nEvery single time we sing the song, they yelling OVDS\nYou know, a man''s gotta do what a man''s gotta do, we''ve done it all\nOnly live large and grind hard so can I get so more? Huh?!\n', '', 261, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-28 15:53:37', '2015-03-12 14:07:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(76275, 35371, 6901, 5, 'Möbius feat. Mako', '', '2014-05-30 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 0, 1, '5.Möbius feat. Mako\n重複在同樣的街 流連同樣的容顏\n藏多少悲歡離別 藏多深刻的情節\n綻開了傷一遍遍 散落的疤痕片片\n無盡的日日夜夜 無盡日日夜夜\n\n重複在同樣的街 留戀同樣的容顏\n藏多少悲歡離別 藏多深刻的情節\n重蹈愛和背叛間 就像花與蝶依戀\n始終不斷尋找 和希望的繾綣\n\nBroken faith will be buried by dust and times\nBroken heart will never be the same again\nWhen your broken soul falls from the paradise \nYou hope someone hold you but  there''s no one waiting for you\nThere''s no one waiting for you\nWaiting for you\n\nDoes god exists?\nThis is my sin, my pills, my drank, my pain make me rhyme this\nThis is the game with only one life, I`m try’na make a living\nThis is the strife, The struggle I left on these fuckin` papers\nThis is my life, my whisper in my ill mind chamber\nSometimes it’s hard to separate and realize these fuckin` fiction\nFact that full of lies, and these fuckin cray conviction\nI got bittersweet but no throne, no answer\nEverything is my victims That is why I never preach, sucka!\n', '', 279, '', '', '', '', '亞神音樂AsiaMuse', '', 0, 1, 0, '2014-05-28 15:57:06', '2015-03-12 14:07:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
